    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine, featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission offers crisp, short-throw shifts, paired with a variable M differential lock for superior corner-exit traction. This example is mechanically robust, with the subframe recently inspected and the cooling system refreshed to ensure thermal efficiency during spirited driving. While the exterior displays minor patina consistent with its age, the chassis remains rigid and the suspension geometry is dialed in for precise turn-in. An authentic driver\u2019s specification for those who value mechanical purity and a 100hp-per-liter performance threshold.",
