      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously cared for and remains in impressive operational and aesthetic shape. The exterior paint retains its deep luster with only minor, expected road wear, while the interior cabin is clean, smoke-free, and features well-preserved upholstery. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly, having benefited from a consistent maintenance schedule\u2014including a recent oil change and a full multi-point inspection. The tires have excellent tread remaining, and the brakes are responsive and firm. It provides a comfortable, dependable driving experience that bridges the gap between everyday utility and refined comfort. Ready for its next owner with all service records available for review.",
